[assistant] Adjusted the native-image compile issue by removing the `UsingReflection` subclass from the public JUnit test class’ nested class tree.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - The native JUnit feature recursively registers declared/nested classes of the test class.
