[assistant] 
[assistant] Fix:
[assistant] - Moved the `UnsafeInjectionHarness`, `Accessor`, and `DispatcherClassLoader` helpers out of the public test class as package-private top-level helper classes in the same Java file.
[assistant] - The public test class now references the helper but no longer declares it as a nested class, avoiding the JUnit native feature’s recursive declared-class scan into ByteBuddy internals.
[assistant] - Kept the dedicated public test class/file for the active dynamic-access class.
[assistant] 
